'''Ready Rations''', commonly known as '''RRs''' were pre-made meals given to [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone soldiers]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. They had a reputation for tasting bad, but were easily portable and provided essential nutrients. There were rumors that the [[Cloning/Legends|clones]] had been genetically conditioned to enjoy them.

